|3 |    └─HASH RIGHT ANTI JOIN NA      |        |
|4 |      ├─EXCHANGE IN DISTR          |        |
|5 |      │ └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (PKEY)|:EX10000|
|6 |      │   └─PX PARTITION ITERATOR  |        |
|7 |      │     └─TABLE FULL SCAN      |t2      |
|8 |      └─PX PARTITION ITERATOR      |        |
|9 |        └─TABLE FULL SCAN          |t1      |
=================================================
